This task developed in swift using 

1- SwiftLint for linting and code formatte  
2- R for handle resources like assets, fonts and colors 
3- RXswift and RXCocoa
4- used abstracted network layer and cacher strategy 
5- MVVM and repository design pattern 
6- Realm for local database handling 
7- configuration environment 
- you can pull to refresh 
